<dl>
    <dt>Open the Camera application</dt>
    <dt>Select the shutter icon</dt>
        <dd>Camera application shall emit sound indicating photo was taken</dd>
        <dd>Camera application shall slide the photo out while it gets ready for the next photo</dd>
    <dt>From the Camera toolbar open the Gallery application</dt>
        <dd>The Gallery application shall open</dd>
        <dd>The Gallery application shall display the recently taken photo</dd>
    <dt>From the Gallery open the Camera application</dt>
        <dd>Bottom swipe raises the toolbar</dd>
        <dd>The Camera application shall open</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
